dosbox
======

# start dosbox under console
SDL_FBDEV=/dev/fb0 SDL_MOUSEDEV=/dev/input/event12 dosbox Games/



mednafen
========

# start mednafen game emulator
mednafen -psx.bios_eu scph7502\(41a\).bin  psx_games/tekken3.cue

# configure gamepad
press ctrl + shift + [n] to select controller type
press alt + shift + [n] to configure buttons/axis
each key needs to be pressed twice
'rapid <key>' is just a key to be configured again for rapid pressing

